<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Reply Notification - E-Learns Platform</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      color: #2c3e50;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #7f8c8d;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>We're excited to let you know that a new reply has been added to your question in the video:</p>
    
    <blockquote style="font-style: italic; border-left: 3px solid #3498db; padding-left: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
      "<%= title %>"
    </blockquote>

    <p>To view the reply and continue the discussion, please visit our platform:</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Thank you for being a valued member of our learning community.</p>
    <p>â€” The E-Learns Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>